text.section:
The Board shall give the following persons notice of the hearing and an opportunity to participate in the hearing:
The claimant;
Each licensee alleged to be responsible for the act or omission giving rise to the claim;
Each unlicensed employee alleged to be responsible for the act or omission giving rise to the claim; and
Each funeral establishment that employs a licensee or unlicensed employee alleged to be responsible for the act or omission giving rise to the claim.
